'''詹姆斯·康诺利'''（{{lang-en|James Connolly}}；{{lang-ga|Séamas Ó Conghaile}}；{{bd|1868年|6月5日|1916年|5月12日|catIdx=C}}），爱尔兰[[社会主义|社会主义]]运动先驱。他出生于[[苏格兰|苏格兰]][[爱丁堡|爱丁堡]][[牛门|牛门]]的一个爱尔兰[[移民|移民]]家庭，11岁时辍学工作，但之后仍然成为当时最杰出的[[马克思主义|马克思主义]]理论家。虽然对自己的爱尔兰背景很自豪，但他也投身于[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]的政治活动中。他因参与1916年[[复活节起义|复活节起义]]而被英军枪决。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
他出生於[[爱丁堡|爱丁堡]][[牛门|牛门]]的愛爾蘭貧民窟中，是約翰·康諾利和瑪麗·麦吉恩的第三個兒子<ref name=jcpbe>{{Cite book | last = Connolly | first = James | author2 = Ellis, Peter Berresford | title = James Connolly: selected writings | publisher = Pluto Press | year = 1988 | location = London | page = 9 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=TGwCEc2DyGgC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA9#v=onepage&q&f=false | isbn = 978-0-7453-0267-6 | access-date = 2020-02-22 | archive-date = 2020-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200524233130/https://books.google.com/books?id=TGwCEc2DyGgC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA9#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他的父母來自愛爾蘭的[[莫纳亨郡|莫纳亨郡]]<ref>{{Cite journal | last = Dangerfield | first = George | title = James Joyce, James Connolly and Irish Nationalism | journal = Irish University Review | volume = 16 | issue = 1 | at=5| date = Spring 1986 | jstor = 25477611 | issn = 0021-1427 }}</ref>。由於出身關係，他終身都帶著一股蘇格蘭口音。<ref>Donal Nevin. 2005. "James Connolly: A Full Life", p. 636 Gill and Macmillan; {{ISBN|0-7171-3911-5}}</ref>

10歲前，他在當地的天主教學校接受教育<ref>{{Cite book | last = Morgan | first = Austen | title = James Connolly : a political biography | publisher = Manchester University Press | year = 1990 | location = Manchester | page = 14 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=8zToAAAAIAAJ&lpg=PP1&pg=PA14#v=onepage&q&f=false | isbn = 978-0-7190-2958-5 | access-date = 2020-02-22 | archive-date = 2020-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200524070952/https://books.google.com/books?id=8zToAAAAIAAJ&lpg=PP1&pg=PA14#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>，之後輟學，成為勞工。14歲入伍（入伍時謊報年齡，並化名里德），加入[[英國陸軍|英國陸軍]]<ref>{{Cite book | last = Edwards | first = Ruth Dudley | title = James Connolly | publisher = Gill and Macmillan | year = 1981 | location = Dublin | pages = 1–2 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=7AM0AAAAMAAJ&q=joined+british+army#search_anchor | isbn = 978-0-7171-1112-1 | access-date = 2020-02-22 | archive-date = 2020-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200522161711/https://books.google.com/books?id=7AM0AAAAMAAJ&q=joined+british+army#search_anchor | dead-url = no }}</ref>皇家蘇格蘭軍團（Royal Scots Regiment）第二營，在愛爾蘭駐扎了七年。
他並不喜歡軍旅生活<ref>Levenson 1973, p. 333</ref>，加上和莉莉·雷諾茲（Lillie Reynolds）的感情發展，當聽說軍團要移駐印度時，他離開了軍隊<ref>{{cite web | last = McCartan | first = Eugene | title = The man looking over our shoulder | work = James Connolly Memorial Lecture | publisher = James Connolly Education Trust | date = 12 May 2006 | url = http://www.iol.ie/~sob/jcet/2006-05-12-emc.html | accessdate = 21 April 2011 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121007073308/http://www.iol.ie/~sob/jcet/2006-05-12-emc.html | archivedate = 2012-10-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1890年4月，他和莉莉在蘇格蘭成婚<ref>Levenson 1973, p. 24</ref>，定居愛丁堡。在那裡，他開始對[[苏格兰社会主义邦联|苏格兰社会主义邦联]]產生興趣<ref>{{Cite book|last=Wallace|first=Martin|title=100 Irish Lives|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|year=1983|location=Lanham, MD|page=[https://archive.org/details/100irishlives00wall/page/147 147]|isbn=978-0-7153-8331-5|url=https://archive.org/details/100irishlives00wall/page/147}}</ref>。

為了家裡的生計，他曾在1895年開過一家補鞋店，但他的修鞋手藝並不好，該店在數月後倒閉<ref>{{cite web|last=Mac Thomáis|first=Shane|title=Remembering the Past – James Connolly|work=anphoblacht.com|publisher=An Phoblacht|date=8 June 2005|url=http://aprnonline.com/?p=58474|accessdate=26 April 2011|archive-date=2012-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312023306/http://aprnonline.com/?p=58474|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>Levenson 1973, p. 39</ref>。

=== 社會主義運動 ===
[[File:Connolly.james.jpg|thumb]]

在他的兄弟約翰被炒魷魚之後，他在1895年接替約翰做了苏格兰社会主义邦联的秘書。此外，他也曾加入[[独立工党|独立工党]]，學習[[世界語|世界語]]。<ref>[http://esperanto.ie/en/ireland/connolly.html James Connolly and Esperanto] {{Wayback|url=http://esperanto.ie/en/ireland/connolly.html |date=20161215171329 }}, esperanto.ie; accessed 28 May 2017</ref>

在都柏林社會主義俱樂部（Dublin Socialist Club）找到一份全職秘書的工作（週薪一鎊）後，他前往都柏林<ref>{{Cite book | last = Kearney | first = Richard | title = The Irish mind: exploring intellectual traditions | publisher = Wolfhound Press | year = 1985 | location = Dublin | page = 200 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=Q7BnAAAAMAAJ&dq=%22dublin+socialist+club%22+job+that+pound+week | isbn = 978-0-391-03311-5 | access-date = 2020-02-22 | archive-date = 2020-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200522182731/https://books.google.com/books?id=Q7BnAAAAMAAJ&dq=%22dublin+socialist+club%22+job+that+pound+week | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book | last = Sheehan | first = Sean | title = Famous Irish Men and Women | publisher = Evans Brothers | year = 2008 | location = London | page = 12 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=ZMI7pODIPGUC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA12#v=onepage&q&f=false | isbn = 978-0-237-53432-5 | access-date = 2020-02-22 | archive-date = 2020-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200524015416/https://books.google.com/books?id=ZMI7pODIPGUC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA12#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在康諾利的指使下，該俱樂部加入了[[爱尔兰社会主义共和党|爱尔兰社会主义共和党]]<ref>{{Cite news | last = Hadden | first = Peter | title = The real ideas of James Connolly | magazine = Socialism Today | location = London | issue = 100 | publisher = Socialist Party (England and Wales) | date = Apr–May 2006 | url = http://www.socialismtoday.org/100/connolly.html | accessdate = 28 April 2011 | archive-date = 2006-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060721041719/http://www.socialismtoday.org/100/connolly.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。同時，他又創辦了報紙《社會主義者》（The Socialist）和社會主義工黨（Socialist Labour Party）。1903年，他前往美國<ref>{{cite book|last1=Greaves|first1=C. Desmond|title=The Life and Times of James Connolly|date=1972|publisher=Lawrence and Wishart|location=London|pages=166–7|edition=2nd|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=j9GfAAAAMAAJ|isbn=978-0853152347|accessdate=11 August 2014|archive-date=2020-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200524013237/https://books.google.com/books?id=j9GfAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，加入了美国[[社会主义劳工党|社会主义劳工党]]（1906）、[[美国社会党_(1901年)|美國社會黨]]（1909）和[[世界产业工人联合会|世界产业工人联合会]]，1907年在紐約成立[[爱尔兰社会主义联盟|爱尔兰社会主义联盟]]，1910年出版《愛爾蘭勞工史》（Labour in Irish History）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.marxists.org/archive/connolly/1910/lih/chap12.htm |title=James Connolly: Labour in Irish History - Chapter 12 |website=Marxists.org |date=2003-12-08 |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2018-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715192548/https://www.marxists.org/archive/connolly/1910/lih/chap12.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1910年他回到愛爾蘭，成為[[詹姆斯·拉金|詹姆斯·拉金]]的左右手，1913年參與[[都柏林大罷工|都柏林大罷工]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.census.nationalarchives.ie/reels/nai000119513/ |title=Census of Ireland 1911 |website=Census.nationalarchives.ie |accessdate=2017-05-28 |archive-date=2018-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424215517/http://www.census.nationalarchives.ie/reels/nai000119513/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一戰爆發後，他成為反戰人士，宣稱：“除了英國政府我不知道這個國家還有什麼外國敵人”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rte.ie/centuryireland/index.php/articles/james-connolly-what-should-irish-people-do-during-the-war|website=RTÉ|title=James Connolly: What should Irish people do during the war?|date=6 November 2016|quote=I know of no foreign enemy of this country except the British Government.|access-date=2020-02-22|archive-date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108093157/https://www.rte.ie/centuryireland/index.php/articles/james-connolly-what-should-irish-people-do-during-the-war|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 去世 ===
[[File:2017-06-20_4904x7356_dublin_kilmainham_gaol_james_connolly_execution.jpg|left]]
他因組織[[復活節起義|復活節起義]]而遭到逮捕，被關押在[[都柏林城堡|都柏林城堡]]中<ref name= costello>{{cite book|last= Costello|first= Peter|year= 1999|page= [https://archive.org/details/dublincastleinli00cost/page/145 145]|title= Dublin Castle, in the life of the Irish nation|publisher= Wolfhound Press|location= Dublin|isbn= 978-0-86327-610-1|url= https://archive.org/details/dublincastleinli00cost/page/145}}</ref>，旋即被判死刑。1916年5月12日，他被帶到[[克瞒汉姆皇家醫院|克瞒汉姆皇家醫院]]，隨後又被帶到[[克瞒汉姆監獄|克瞒汉姆監獄]]，並在此處決。<ref name= emmons>{{cite book|last= Emmons|first= David M. |year= 2012|page= 480|title= Beyond the American Pale: The Irish in the West|publisher= University of Oklahoma Press|location= U.S.A}}</ref><ref name= seumas>{{cite book|last= MacManus|first= Seumas |year= 2005|page= 696|title= The Story of the Irish Race|publisher= Cosimo, Inc|location= Ireland}}</ref>

被處決前康諾利其實就已經由於傷勢嚴重而時日無多，醫生說他頂多也就能再活一兩天了。但政府仍然決定執行槍決，他被綁在椅子上，行刑隊朝他開火，將其殺害<ref name="Death Registration">{{cite web |url=https://civilrecords.irishgenealogy.ie/churchrecords/images/deaths_returns/deaths_1916/05245/4453541.pdf |title=Registered Deaths in South Dublin, 1916 |website=irishgenealogy.ie |at=04453541, 477, Entry Numbers 1–10 |access-date=22 September 2018 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202170738/https://civilrecords.irishgenealogy.ie/churchrecords/images/deaths_returns/deaths_1916/05245/4453541.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

